snippet.title: Official Everwild Eternals Trailer - Xbox Games Showcase July 2020
snippet.description:
"Our world has a rhythm. We all sense it, but only a few truly feel it."

Take a fresh glimpse at some of the natural and magical elements that await in Everwild, a new world in creation at Rare Ltd.
